00:21:12.680 --> 00:21:13.952
I had this amazing experience.

00:21:13.952 --> 00:21:16.410
So I went out to Long Beach,
and sat with the Racing Rivals

00:21:16.410 --> 00:21:18.930
team, and helped
them design the game.

00:21:18.930 --> 00:21:21.730
And I guarantee you,
beyond just engaging

00:21:21.730 --> 00:21:24.110
those players and their friends
in a deeper, deeper level

00:21:24.110 --> 00:21:25.834
in the game, that word spread.

